OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fand bright this evening, though a few
OL,7,Fspots of rain not to be ruled out,
OL,8,Fmainly across Tayside. A risk of
OL,9,Ffurther showers towards dawn.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMainly cloudy in the morning
OL,12,Fwith a few showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,13,FTurning brighter but with a risk of
OL,14,Ffurther showers in the afternoon, some
OL,15,Fpossibly heavy and thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
