OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled throughout this period.
OL,7,FThere'll be plenty of good sunny
OL,8,Fspells inland, especially during
OL,9,Fafternoons, however areas of cloud
OL,10,Fwill often affect coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
